# Enforce LF line endings in the repository for all text files.
# Rationale: this project's integrity rests on GPG signatures and OpenTimestamps
# hashes over canonical bytes. A CRLF/LF flip after signing or stamping would
# invalidate those without any visible source change. We normalize to LF on
# commit regardless of the checkout platform (Windows tooling may still touch
# these files). See docs/ pre-registration for the WHO/WHEN integrity model.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly binary — never normalize, never diff as text.
*.ots    binary
*.asc    -text
*.pdf    binary
*.png    binary
*.jpg    binary
*.gz     binary
*.zip    binary
